(enableSFBOpt, power_leakage).explanation: Enabling store-to-load forwarding buffer optimization adds additional circuitry and logic gates that contribute to static power consumption through leakage currents;

(enableSFBOpt, area_cell_area).explanation: Store-to-load forwarding buffer optimization requires additional hardware components and logic circuits that directly increase the physical silicon area occupied by cells;

(enableSFBOpt, nDCacheMSHRs).explanation: Store-to-load forwarding buffer optimization operates at the execution pipeline level and does not directly determine the number of data cache miss status holding registers;
